<a name="generate"></a>Generate an AES-256 Key
======================

    keytool -genseckey -alias jceksaes -keyalg AES -keysize 256 -storetype JCEKS -keypass mykeypass -storetype jceks -keystore aes-keystore.jck -storepass mystorepass


